---
import PageShell from '../../../../components/PageShell.astro';
import CTABox from '../../../../components/CTABox.astro';
import ComparisonTable from '../../../../components/ComparisonTable.astro';

const tocItems = [
  { id: 'overview', text: 'SafetyWing in Italy', level: 2 },
  { id: 'plans-and-pricing', text: 'Plans and Pricing', level: 2 },
  { id: 'italy-benefits', text: 'Italy-Specific Benefits', level: 2 },
  { id: 'limitations', text: 'Important Limitations', level: 2 },
  { id: 'who-its-for', text: 'Who Should Choose SafetyWing', level: 2 },
];

const relatedLinks = [
  { title: 'Health Insurance in Italy', href: '/countries/italy/insurance' },
  { title: 'SafetyWing Review', href: '/providers/safetywing' },
  { title: 'SafetyWing vs Cigna', href: '/compare/safetywing-vs-cigna-global' },
];

const planColumns = [
  { key: 'plan', header: 'Plan' },
  { key: 'coverage', header: 'Coverage' },
  { key: 'italyPrice', header: 'Italy Price' },
];

const planRows = [
  { plan: 'Nomad Insurance', coverage: 'Travel medical', italyPrice: '€45/mo' },
  { plan: 'Remote Health', coverage: 'Comprehensive health', italyPrice: '€180-250/mo' },
];
---

<PageShell
  title="SafetyWing Insurance in Italy"
  description="Guide to using SafetyWing in Italy. Affordable nomad insurance, limitations, and when it's the right choice."
  headline="SafetyWing Insurance in Italy"
  subheadline="SafetyWing for digital nomads in Italy—affordable coverage, but understand the limitations before you buy."
  heroBackgroundImage="/images/countries/italy-hero-bg.png"
  tocItems={tocItems}
  relatedLinks={relatedLinks}
  ctaButtonText="Get SafetyWing"
  ctaButtonHref="/providers/safetywing"
>
  <h2 id="overview">SafetyWing in Italy</h2>
  <p>
    SafetyWing has become popular with digital nomads for its affordable pricing and nomad-friendly design. However, it's important to understand the difference between their Nomad Insurance (travel medical) and Remote Health (comprehensive health insurance).
  </p>
  <p>
    For Italy's digital nomad visa, SafetyWing Nomad Insurance alone may not meet requirements—you may need Remote Health or a different insurer.
  </p>

  <div class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg p-6 my-6">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-amber-900 mb-2">Visa Compliance Warning</h3>
    <p class="text-amber-800">
      SafetyWing Nomad Insurance is travel medical insurance, not comprehensive health insurance. Verify with the Italian consulate whether it meets digital nomad visa requirements. Remote Health is more likely to be accepted.
    </p>
  </div>

  <CTABox
    title="Get SafetyWing"
    description="See SafetyWing pricing for digital nomads."
    buttonText="Get Quote"
    buttonHref="/providers/safetywing"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <h2 id="plans-and-pricing">Plans and Pricing</h2>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={planColumns} rows={planRows} />
  </div>

  <h3>Nomad Insurance vs Remote Health</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Nomad Insurance (~€45/mo):</strong> Travel medical—good for emergencies, limited for routine care</li>
    <li><strong>Remote Health (~€180-250/mo):</strong> Comprehensive health insurance—better for long-term residents</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="italy-benefits">Italy-Specific Benefits</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Affordable:</strong> Significantly cheaper than traditional insurers</li>
    <li><strong>Nomad-designed:</strong> Built for location-independent workers</li>
    <li><strong>Flexible:</strong> Monthly subscription, cancel anytime</li>
    <li><strong>Home country coverage:</strong> Some coverage when visiting home</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="limitations">Important Limitations</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Nomad Insurance is travel medical:</strong> Not comprehensive health insurance</li>
    <li><strong>Coverage limits:</strong> Lower than traditional insurers</li>
    <li><strong>Pre-existing conditions:</strong> Not covered under Nomad Insurance</li>
    <li><strong>Visa compliance:</strong> May not meet Italian visa requirements</li>
    <li><strong>Network:</strong> Smaller provider network than major insurers</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="who-its-for">Who Should Choose SafetyWing in Italy</h2>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-900 mb-3">Good Fit</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-green-800">
        <li>Digital nomads on short stays</li>
        <li>Budget-conscious travelers</li>
        <li>Those with other primary coverage (SSN)</li>
        <li>Young, healthy individuals</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Consider Alternatives</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
        <li>Digital nomad visa applicants (verify compliance)</li>
        <li>Those with pre-existing conditions</li>
        <li>Expats wanting comprehensive coverage</li>
        <li>Families (limited coverage)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <CTABox
    title="Compare Your Options"
    description="Make sure you choose the right coverage for your Italy plans."
    buttonText="Compare All Plans"
    buttonHref="/best/expat-health-insurance"
    variant="highlight"
  />
</PageShell>
